{"tid":1245403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 聽日究竟衝定唔衝?","createTime":"2019-06-20T09:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T14:59:17.000Z","uid":190579,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfdcd6ca5df05968d5714766222166ebb1a1113","tid":1245403,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"我認為極端地和理，或極端地勇武都係不利，要取<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">中庸之道</span></strong>，最好就係<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">同612一樣， 唔需要真係食贏克驚，只要向世界展現出對野餐嘅熱情決心，以低於克驚一級嘅食量，迫克驚食滯自己嘔返出嚟就得</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">取自:<br />\n&lt;&lt;夢見嚟緊最大型野餐係621明日大嶼開會日&gt;&gt;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234173</a></span><br />\n<br />\n經69, 616 之役之後，相信大家都好明白民意係無法<span style=\"color: blue;\">直接</span>比壓力林奠<br />\n而衝都<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔可以</span>直接比壓力林奠，林奠同建制搵個安全既地方匿埋就冇事<br />\n即係話，無論衝定唔衝，都只能<span style=\"color: gold;\">間接</span>地制造壓力。如下圖示意:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1) 國際(制裁)&gt;中央&gt;林奠政府<br />\n2) 國際(制裁)&gt;建制&gt;林奠政府<br />\n3) 本地輿論&gt;建制(擔心選情)&gt;林奠政府<br />\n4) 商界&gt;建制&gt;林奠政府</span><br />\n<br />\n612的確係比左壓力林奠，但都係<span style=\"color: red;\">間接</span>性。主因係D狗開無雙，反襯<span style=\"color: gold;\">相對</span>和平既示威者，上哂全世界既報，透過1,2,3) 比左壓力林奠<br />\n換言之，如果想成功複製612，克驚就需要開無雙，咁先有<span style=\"color: red;\">新聞價值</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">制裁理由</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">雖然可能你會覺得咁講有D冷血，攞第一排義士安全嚟較飛，食緊人血饅頭<br />\n但我想講，外國傳媒某程度上就係食緊我地人血饅頭！如果要借助佢地既力量，就要比佢地食，製造新聞價值同話題比佢地去煲大件事。</span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n極端和理弊處:</span></ins><br />\n1) 總有勇武想做D野，如果見冇人跟/幫/支援，佢地會好唔開心<br />\n嚴重既話可能會灰心喪志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者屌尻哂你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個唔係佢地既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 和理就算唔想衝都應該永遠做勇武最堅實既後援<br />\n2) 同狗鬥坐，就引唔到佢地醜陋一面出嚟，比機會佢地洗底，同造成政府已經讓步同克制既錯覺<br />\n3) 我地唔需要<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對</span>和平，<span style=\"color: gold;\">相對</span>和平已經足夠外國傳媒同政府出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>極端勇武弊處:</ins></span><br />\n1) 增加被捕風險，削弱長期抗爭力量<br />\n2) 一個唔覺意暴力過狗/做咗D有位比人入既事，輿論就會大逆轉，亦會失去和理既G持<br />\n3) 增加受傷風險<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論、補充。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">最後利申番: 之前有野餐，有緊貼頭排支援，有食過煙，有幫過人，已經請咗假聽日再野餐。如果唔係咁，我會覺得自己冇資格講呢D野</span>"},{"pid":"ee061b1daca407e97528fb8502b8aae110e860b0","tid":1245403,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b7bec46a44e7570030fa9bb97e6ae4cd2d933d8","tid":1245403,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n4個地點步程10分鐘內：禮賓 政總 警總等 <br />\n<br />\n人未齊未衝得做咩好？ 唔好阻人返工！！！<br />\n香港人平時唔係好想打風有假放既咩？ 而家比個藉口大家聽日無工返就屌曬聲？<br />\n利申發夢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!<br />\n新目標：將香港帶到G20 AGENDA!!!!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其他野可以遲d做無所謂 <strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">G20呢d大好機會錯失左就一世</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9dba22b89ab4a1efb68728bf81d00e7dd3d59850","tid":1245403,"uid":107297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"唔好掟磚唔好玩鐵就得"},{"pid":"93093cecad9c8484c22e3b71a1133b9d5bcd3950","tid":1245403,"uid":161626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a><br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"56ed4e75267abea59ef346b5991c1fb7912ecc0b","tid":1245403,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:39:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>不勸，不阻<br />\n不說教，不煩膠<br />\n不以為自己叻 L 晒<br />\n不譴責，不割蓆<br />\n責任在林鄭</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f61e556295cdb5c45299d686061ef0802af43f0a","tid":1245403,"uid":1400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多，去咗集會先講<br />\n唔夠人你衝條撚"},{"pid":"4ce89d122f46b22c8ae0981bed1c84b51801748b","tid":1245403,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61e556295cdb5c45299d686061ef0802af43f0a","tid":1245403,"uid":1400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多，去咗集會先講<br />\n唔夠人你衝條撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"啱 唔理衝唔衝 聽日去金鐘"},{"pid":"a69825e84ea08bb7a89ca81af50b13ad872cc08e","tid":1245403,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtUNUoH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtUNUoH.png&h=dd4a5bdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"915c82a07935f0458b38b6d3439434f9f29e85f1","tid":1245403,"uid":54220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"988bc810af2cdeffd537f92fdb00d8b30c1cf32a","tid":1245403,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62215140c5b136d84a90abfd9a470537902fda3d","tid":1245403,"uid":161430,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T09:44:48.0